  * [ Strategic and International Policy ](https://www.asd.gov.au/careers/career-opportunities/strategic-and-international-policy)

  

All successful candidates commence their training program on a salary of
$74,796 plus a 4% service allowance and 15.4% superannuation. On successful
completion, graduates will advance to a higher salary dependent on which
training pathway has been completed.

